title: Be a Honest Sinner than Lying Hypocrit

description:
Today on the show we had author Robert Greene call in where he speaks on critiques to culture, fear, redemption, Malcolm X and more. Also they had actress Cynthia Erivo call in and spoke on The Essence Of Aretha Franklin, Diversity In Hollywood, New Music and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to former Louisiana Priest, along with 2 dominatrices arrested and charged with vandalism after having threesome at the alter. Also, Angela nominated track runner Alison Felix for Woman's History Month.
